Nonlinear data

Source: vignettes/cardinalr08nonlinear.Rmd
cardinalr08nonlinear.Rmd
library(cardinalR)
library(langevitour)
curvy_data <- two_curvilinear_data_with_noise(sample_size = 600, 
                                              num_noise_dims = 2, 
                                              min_noise = -0.05, max_noise = 0.05)

colnames(curvy_data) <- paste0("x", 1:NCOL(curvy_data))

langevitour(curvy_data, pointSize = 2)
swiss_data <- swiss_roll(sample_size = 200, num_noise_dims = 2, 
                         min_noise = -0.05, max_noise = 0.05)

colnames(swiss_data) <- paste0("x", 1:NCOL(swiss_data))

langevitour(swiss_data, pointSize = 2)
